title: Glen Campbell 1972.01.11 Johnny Cash; Merle Haggard [Tdot]
description:
Glen's guests are Johnny Cash, June Carter Cash, Merle Haggard, Buck Owens, Freddie Hart, Jerry Reed and Minnie Pearl.

Musical Highlights: Glen sings "For the Good Times". Johnny Cash sings "A Thing Called Love". Johnny Cash & June Carter perform "No Need to Worry".

Merle Haggard sings "Carolyn". Freddie Hart sings "Easy Lovin'". Jerry Reed performs "Another Puff".

Johnny & Glen duet on "Folsom Prison Blues". Glen, Johnny, Merle, Buck, Jerry, Larry McNeeley do a medley: "A Boy Named Sue", "I've Got a Tiger By the Tail", "When You're Hot You're Hot", "I Take a Lot of Pride in What I Am" & "Born to Lose"
